    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection, consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and mechanical systems are functioning as they should, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. It has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
